description: Just moments from the beach and Broadway, this pet-friendly stylish two-bedroom condo offers two levels of well-appointed living and LOW CONDO FEE. The main level features a sun-splashed living room with gas fireplace, oversized east-facing windows and a seamless flow into the eat-in, stainless steel kitchen with gas stove—perfect for everyday living and entertaining. A powder room completes the first level. Step out into your private fenced backyard with composite decking, ideal for summer gatherings, grilling and chilling. The lower level offers two generous bedrooms, a refreshed full bath, and in-unit laundry for added convenience. Located in the heart of South Boston, enjoy easy access to vibrant shops, dining, public transit, and major highways.
